\nand of the physical scales introduced by the galaxy formation process.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 19 Dec 2016 20:05:21 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 10 May 2017 21:39:06 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 26 Jun 2017 23:46:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-08-09"}
