 flow for the\nSn-transport and nonequilibrium-diffusion radiation solutions, and show that\nthere are considerable differences in the radiation flow between these models\nacross the shock structure. Finally, we analyze the radiation flow to\nunderstand the cause of the adaptation zone, as well as the structure of the\nSn-transport radiation-intensity solutions across the shock structure.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 19 Dec 2016 20:46:48 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 23 Feb 2017 18:35:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-04-05"}
