azars. Finally, the\ntemperature of the electrons in the shocked plasma is shown to be a degenerated\nquantity for different magentizations of the ejected material.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 19 Dec 2016 21:00:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 21 Feb 2017 20:27:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-04-12"}
