nizing background with different prescriptions of\n$f_{\\rm esc} (M_{\\rm UV})$. We show that the understanding of the luminosity\ndependence hinges on the ability to constrain the escape fraction down to\n$M_{\\rm UV} \\sim -18$ mag in the future.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 19 Dec 2016 21:00:18 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 22 Feb 2017 19:00:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-04-12"}
